data.description: MUST SEE this Beautiful, well maintained 4 bedroom, 2 full bath brick Cape Cod home located on Youngstown's West side near Chaney High School. with 1 bedroom & 1 bath on first floor then remaining bedrooms and bath on upper levels. Home features hardwood floors and some carpet throughout, fireplace, fully equipped kitchen, classic built-in cabinets & bookshelves. Full basement boasts open rec room area & laundry room.  Make your appointment today before it's gone!
